name: Inside Sense Group
description:
Inside Sense is a dynamic and forward-thinking talent and event management agency; a brainchild of Dj and producer Cihan Mareno. The firm operates on the basis that artists need more than just a cold, calculating manager or consultant, but a true team player, somebody passionate and hard-working to join the family.

Inside Sense represent artists on an international level, catering to some of the hottest clubs and outdoor festivals around.
